latestIgtvVideos.title: One outfit, 4 different occasions sorted⚡️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Soo here I am after a long break. 
Firstly would like to thank you guys for keeping a continuous check on me and asking if I am alright. Well tears shed every single day, but I guess life is all about going with the flow with courage and kindness. ✨So here’s the video where one single outfit can sort your 4 occasions. 4 style and 4 favourite music 🎵 tracks.Played with hair, makeup and accessories. Have not played with  any piece of clothes just a single outfit and no confusion.
✨Date Night: Open hair, Red Lips, shimmery sling,Stilleto, loads of accessories and have a great time ✨Brunch Scene: Half pony, added just rings no bracelets, kitten heels, a tiny sling and good to go
✨Work Waves: Sleek pony, formal heels, classic bag and a statement earrings  and ready to beat off others💕
✨Casual Outings: Low pony with head band on, flats, glasses on, with bag good to go
.
.
.
.
